@feinstein It seems like the real issue is the debug connection closing when it isn't supposed to. Can you give us any more info about what is going on that causes it to close? If you can share a log file that might help.

@jmagman Sorry, but I'm not sure who best to ask this. Is the team in general happy with the time required to build and install an app? It seems to me that two minutes is quite a long time for that.

@devoncarew @jacob314 To answer the original question, you may have a better perspective than me. Do you think it is feasible to detect a running app and connect to it?
